casebody.data:
A.S.E., petitioner,
v.
A.S. No. 13-371. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 2, 2013.

Motion of Family Defense Center, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of Sargent Shriver National Center on Poverty Law for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Texas, Ninth District, denied.
